snippet.title: Fishing Planet - Announce Teaser | PS4
snippet.description:
Fishing Planet is a unique and highly realistic online first-person multiplayer fishing simulator, that’s coming soon to PS4! Now you don’t have to choose between heading out on a fishing trip or staying home to enjoy playing your console. Fishing Planet takes your favorite hobby and brings it right to your living room. So prepare to indulge in the fantastic world of fishing without having to leave your couch, a fishing adventure that’s absolutely free and requires only your console!

http://www.fishingplanet.com
